17
00:02:09,479 --> 00:02:12,120
For a long time after my parents passed away,

18
00:02:12,760 --> 00:02:14,640
I was irritable and negative,

19
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:16,090
full of self-blame.

20
00:02:17,079 --> 00:02:19,610
These emotions stayed with me for a long time,

21
00:02:20,240 --> 00:02:21,640
