34
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:16,300
It was never your fault to begin with.

35
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,480
Besides,

36
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:19,200
the Lu Hui I see

37
00:03:19,600 --> 00:03:21,930
