38
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:33,010
Do you know when I first drank alcohol?

39
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:35,800
It was that same year,

40
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,840
during the Mid-Autumn Festival.

41
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,240
My mom went to bed early,

42
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,920
