52
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,120
Back then, my dad told me,

53
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,480
'Life is just a couple of drinks,

54
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:12,160
and in the end, all worries disappear.'

55
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:14,680
No matter what happens,

56
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:17,440
never hide it in your heart.

57
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:20,279
Have a couple of drinks, get some sleep,

58
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:22,680
and when you wake up,

59
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,920
if something can be solved,

60
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,360
go solve it right away.

61
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:28,610
For things you can't solve,

62
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:30,610
