63
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,440
there's always a way.

64
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,680
Your uncle lived with such clarity.

65
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:47,480
It's been a long time since I celebrated any holidays.

66
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,480
Me too.

67
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:52,960
I think that,

68
